[size=4][b]What[/b][/size]

[size=3]Gives you control over when and how fast the body-delivery donkey arrives at the graveyard. Vanilla runs a single delivery on a fixed schedule; this mod lets you run the donkey multiple times per day and bumps his walking speed so he actually reaches the drop-off before the day ends.[/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][b]Flexible delivery schedule[/b] — independent toggles for Morning, Day, Evening, and Night deliveries. Enable any combination; disable them all to pause body income.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Donkey speed slider[/b] — the mod's default is slightly faster than vanilla. The game's default speed can cause the donkey to despawn before reaching the graveyard in some save states; the boost is there to stop that from happening. Adjustable in the config.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Replaces the vanilla delivery[/b] — the one-shot vanilla delivery is disabled while this mod is installed. All body income flows through the mod's schedule.[/size]
[*][size=3]No unlock gating — applies as soon as you have the donkey unlocked in the main story (the point where vanilla would have started delivering).[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Other mods of mine you might like[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/53]Longer Days[/url] — pairs perfectly. Longer Days stretches the day cycle so you have more time to process each delivery before the next arrives.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/52]Thoughtful Reminders[/url] — daily thought-text so you never lose track of the day cycle or upcoming deliveries.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/89]Grave Changes Redux[/url] — lifts the quality cap on graves/decorations so the increased body throughput actually pays off in higher-quality graveyard scores.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/49]Add Straight To Table[/url] — skips the autopsy-table confirmation dialog. Handy when processing many bodies per day.[/size]
[/list]
[size=4][b]Configuration[/b][/size]

[size=3]If you installed the required [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/79]Graveyard Keeper BepInEx 5 Pack[/url] and this mod is configurable, press F1 in-game to open the config interface.[/size]

[size=4][b]Requirements[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/79][size=3]Graveyard Keeper BepInEx 5 Pack at Graveyard Keeper Nexus - Mods and community (nexusmods.com)[/size][/url]
[/list]
[size=4][b]Installation[/b][/size]

[size=3]Installation using Vortex is the recommended installation method. If you wish to install manually, extract the contents of the mod archive into:

[code]...&#92;steamapps&#92;common&#92;Graveyard Keeper&#92;BepInEx[/code][/size]

